body:
These sample queries use the following index definition on the collection:

```json
{
  "mappings": {
    "dynamic": true,
    "fields": {
      "items": [
        {
          "dynamic": true,
          "type": "embeddedDocuments"
        },
        {
          "dynamic": true,
          "fields": {
            "tags": {
              "type": "token"
            }
          },
          "type": "document"
        }
      ],
      "purchaseMethod": {
        "type": "token"
      }
    }
  }
}
```
